\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5562974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5562974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104epb1702547154823.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epb1702547154823.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epb1702547154823.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"epb1702547154823\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Auto-indent is an automated feature in the Uniface Script Editor that automatically\n\t\tadjusts the indentation of Proc lines, ensuring consistent and readable formatting. This\n\t\tfeature is enabled by default and can be disabled by setting <code class=\"ph codeph\">autoindent=off</code>\n\t\tin the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">When pressing <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">Enter</kbd> at the end of a line, auto-indent will\n\t\t\tautomatically add indentation to the new line. The new line will have the same\n\t\t\tindentation as the line above. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">If the line above starts a new scope, such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">if</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">for</code>,\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">while</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">variables</code>, etc., then the new line will\n\t\t\thave an additional tab or spaces. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">If the line above terminates a scope, such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">endif</code>,\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">endfor</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">endwhile</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">endvariables</code>,\n\t\t\tetc., then the line above will also be auto indented.</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"epb1702547154823__note_x3v_h35_tzb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> There are a few limitations with auto-indentation:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"epb1702547154823__ul_zrm_335_tzb\">\n<li class=\"li\">The HTML language, JavaScript blocks, and blockdata blocks do not support\n\t\t\t\t\t\tauto-indentation.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">When using inline-if statements or inline-while statements, always make sure\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthat brackets surround the conditional statements.</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p\">To ensure that new lines are automatically indented, edit the Script Editor definition in\n\t\t\tthe <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file and ensure that <code class=\"ph codeph\">autoindent</code> is\n\t\t\tset as <code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> as shown below:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104epb1702547154823_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"epb1702547154823__codeblock_q5c_t35_tzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;usys.ini\n[widgets]\n...\nSourceEdit=usrcedit(font=procboxfont;language=uniface;autoindent=on)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"epb1702547154823__ul_c5f_535_tzb\">\n<li class=\"li\">Autoindent— new lines will be automatically indented; default is on.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5562974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5562974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Configuring the auto-indentation feature Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Auto-indent is an automated feature in the Uniface Script Editor that automatically adjusts the indentation of Proc lines, ensuring consistent and readable formatting. This feature is enabled by default and can be disabled by setting autoindent=off in the usys.ini file. When pressing Enter at the end of a line, auto-indent will automatically add indentation to the new line. The new line will have the same indentation as the line above. If the line above starts a new scope, such as if , for , while , variables , etc., then the new line will have an additional tab or spaces. If the line above terminates a scope, such as endif , endfor , endwhile , endvariables , etc., then the line above will also be auto indented. Note: There are a few limitations with auto-indentation: The HTML language, JavaScript blocks, and blockdata blocks do not support auto-indentation. When using inline-if statements or inline-while statements, always make sure that brackets surround the conditional statements. To ensure that new lines are automatically indented, edit the Script Editor definition in the usys.ini file and ensure that autoindent is set as on as shown below: Explain this code ;usys.ini [widgets] ... SourceEdit=usrcedit(font=procboxfont;language=uniface;autoindent=on) Copy Autoindent— new lines will be automatically indented; default is on. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}